# assets/ Directory

## Purpose
User-provided brand assets, images, logos, and fonts.

## Rules
- User uploads assets per-session (not committed to repo)
- Store in `state/` subdirectory with session reference
- Validate file types before use: SVG, PNG, JPG, WEBP, GIF
- No asset fetching from external URLs without user consent

## V1 Constraints
- No stock photo fetching
- No external font CDN (system fonts only)
- No user-uploaded executable files
